void init(){_fac[0]=fac[0]=1;rep(i,1,sz-1) _fac[i]=inv(fac[i]=fac[i-1]*i%mod);}
ll C(int n,int m){return n>=m&&m>=0?fac[n]*_fac[m]%mod*_fac[n-m]%mod:0;}

int n,m;
char s[sz];
int a[sz],K;
int vis[sz],ed[sz];
ll ans;

bool check()
{
	rep(i,1,m) vis[i]=0;
	int l=1,r=1,c=0;
	rep(i,1,K)
	{
		if (a[i]==1) { ++c; continue; }
		while (l<=m&&(vis[l]||s[l]=='b')) ++l;
		chkmax(r,l+1);
		while (r<=m&&(vis[r]||s[r]=='r')) ++r;
		if (r>m) return 0;
		vis[l]=vis[r]=1;ed[i]=r;
	}
	int cc=c;
	rep(i,1,m) if (cc&&s[i]=='r'&&!vis[i]) vis[i]=1,--cc;
	if (cc) return 0;
	int pos=1;
	rep(i,1,K)
	{
		if (a[i]==1) break;
		chkmax(pos,ed[i]);
		cc=a[i]-2;
		while (pos<=m&&cc) cc-=(!vis[pos]),++pos;
		if (cc) return 0;
	}
	return 1;
}
void work()
{
	if (!check()) return;
	ll ret=fac[K];
	for (int l=1,r;l<=K;l=r+1)
	{
		for (r=l;r<K&&a[r+1]==a[r];++r);
		ret=ret*_fac[r-l+1]%mod;
	}
	int sum=K-1; rep(i,1,K) sum+=(a[i]==1?1:a[i]*2-3);
	int c=2; rep(i,1,K) c+=2*(a[i]!=1);
	ret=ret*C(n+c-1,sum+c-1)%mod;
	(ans+=ret)%=mod;
}

void dfs(int m,int lst,int sum)
{
	if (K-1+sum>n) return;
	work();
	drep(i,min(m,lst),1) a[++K]=i,dfs(m-i,i,sum+(i==1?1:i*2-3)),a[K--]=0;
}

